該片自2008年起一直由[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]公司籌劃<ref name=Variety1 />。2009年8月，它宣布由丹和凱文·哈格曼編寫成一個動作冒險和喜劇的電影劇本<ref>{{cite news|last=Graser|first=Marc|title=Warner builds pic with Lego|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118007162|accessdate=2011-11-12|newspaper=Variety|date=2009-08-11|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111120234751/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118007162|archivedate=2011-11-20}}</ref>。2010年6月，《[[食破天驚|食破天驚]]》導演[[菲爾·洛德與克里斯多福·米勒|菲爾·洛德與克里斯多福·米勒]]被僱用為編劇和導演<ref>{{cite news|last=McNary|first=Dave|title='Cloudy' directors toy with 'Lego'|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118021180|accessdate=2011-11-12|newspaper=Variety|date=2010-06-28|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120119105130/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118021180|archivedate=2012-01-19}}</ref>。2011年11月，[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]表示該片將於2014年發表，電影的80％預算將用於由澳大利亞 Animal Logic製作動畫，而《[[機器雞|機器雞]]》的主任克里斯·麥凱也會加入和米勒共同執導本片<ref name=Variety1>{{cite news|last=McNary|first=Dave|title=Warners greenlights 'Lego' feature|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118046055|accessdate=2011-11-12|newspaper=Variety|date=2011-11-11|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111113055417/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118046055|archivedate=2011-11-13}}</ref>。2012年3月，米勒透露了影片的標題定為「Lego: The Piece of Resistance」，而故事是關於：「涉及多重樂高玩具世界觀。主角在多個不同的世界中被一個邪惡暴君凍結定型，成為宇宙中的所謂最合格樂高人物」<ref>{{cite news|last=Han|first=Angie|title=Phil Lord and Chris Miller Offer New Title, Plot Details for Warner Bros.' Lego Movie|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/phil-lord-chris-miller-offer-title-plot-details-warner-bros-lego-movie/|accessdate=2012-03-05|newspaper=Slash Film|date=2012-03-05|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120306165827/http://www.slashfilm.com/phil-lord-chris-miller-offer-title-plot-details-warner-bros-lego-movie/|archivedate=2012-03-06}}</ref>。2012年4月，華納兄弟公司決定電影於2014年2月28日上映<ref>{{cite news|last=McNary|first=Dave|title=Warner Bros. dates 'Lego,' '42'|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118053005|accessdate=2012-04-24|newspaper=Variety|date=2012-04-23|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120531052411/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118053005|archivedate=2012-05-31}}</ref>。

2012年6月公佈配音名單，克里斯·普拉特為主角艾密特配音，威爾·阿奈特為樂高蝙蝠俠配音，而樂高超人的角色由查尼·泰坦配音<ref name=VarietySupeVoices/>。2012年8月，據透露，伊麗莎白·班克與摩根·弗里曼將分別為露西（後改名為溫斯黛）和一位古老又神祕的魔法師維特長老配音<ref name=ComingSoonCast>{{cite news|title=Casting and Plot Details Confirmed for LEGO|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=94156|accessdate=2012-08-29|newspaper=ComingSoon.net|date=2012-08-28|author=Warner Bros.|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103191012/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=94156|archivedate=2012-11-03}}</ref>。影片講述艾密特的故事，他是一個身材迷你、依法中規中矩又普通的樂高人物，卻被誤認為是最不尋常的建築大師。他起初遇上維特長老、溫斯黛和蝙蝠俠，在樂高宇宙一起阻止一個邪惡的暴君<ref name=VarietySupeVoices>{{cite news|last=Sneider|first=Jeff|title=Super voices in play for WB's Lego movie|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118055994|accessdate=2012-06-26|newspaper=Variety|date=2012-06-26|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120629032823/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118055994|archivedate=2012-06-29}}</ref><ref name=ComingSoonCast />。在2012年10月，華納兄弟公司將影片的發布日期更改，還簡單題為「樂高」，至2014年2月7日<ref>{{cite news|title=Warner Bros Shifts ''Lego'' Release Date|url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/10/lego-release-date-change-february-7-2014-warner-bros/|accessdate=2012-10-22|newspaper=Deadline|date=2012-10-22|author=The Deadline Team|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023150207/http://www.deadline.com/2012/10/lego-release-date-change-february-7-2014-warner-bros/|archivedate=2012-10-23}}</ref>。在2012年11月，愛麗森·布里、威爾·法洛、連恩·尼遜和尼克·奧弗曼簽署了當中的角色。布里表達了艾密特的團隊具有強大的秘密成員，法洛聲演反派——企業總裁，尼遜聲演壞警察的敵人，而奧弗曼則聲演一個要向總裁報復的海盜鬍鬚鋼<ref>{{cite news|last=Chitwood|first=Adam|title=Nick Offerman Talks THE LEGO MOVIE; Says He Plays a Pirate Named Metalbeard and Compares Film to THE WIZARD OF OZ or WILLY WONKA|url=http://collider.com/nick-offerman-lego-movie-interview/|accessdate=2013-01-30|newspaper=Collider.com|date=2013-01-28|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130130235752/http://collider.com/nick-offerman-lego-movie-interview/|archivedate=2013-01-30}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Warner Bros Shifts ''Lego'' Release Date|url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/11/will-ferrell-liam-neeson-lego-movie-casting-warner-bros/|accessdate=2012-11-09|newspaper=Deadline|date=2012-11-09|author=The Deadline Team|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121110011025/http://www.deadline.com/2012/11/will-ferrell-liam-neeson-lego-movie-casting-warner-bros/|archivedate=2012-11-10}}</ref>。2013年3月21日，它宣布了電影的正式名字是「樂高大電影」<ref name=ComingSoonCast2>{{cite news|title=Title Treatment and Contest for The LEGO Movie|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=101851|accessdate=2013-03-21|newspaper=ComingSoon.net|date=2013-03-21|author=Warner Bros.|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130325045535/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=101851|archivedate=2013-03-25}}</ref>。

2012年7月，在LEGO官方Facebook專頁舉辦了一場比賽，優勝的樂高車輛參賽作品將會出現在電影中<ref>{{cite news|title=Welcome to the official Facebook page for LEGO: The Motion Picture...|url=http://www.facebook.com/LegoMovie/posts/331154633637332|accessdate=2012-08-29|newspaper=Facebook|date=2012-07-12|author=LEGO: The Motion Picture|quote=Welcome to the official Facebook page for LEGO: The Motion Picture, in theaters 2014! We're kicking things off with a contest for all you creative LEGO builders out there. Design your very own LEGO vehicle for the chance to have it appear in the upcoming movie! Watch the video below from directors Phil Lord and Chris Miller, and learn more about the contest here}}</ref>。後來公佈有17個樂高積木組的場景和人物將被採用<ref name=CSComicCon />，包括企業的「邪惡巢穴」<ref name=THREvilLair>{{cite news|last=Kit|first=Borys|title=First-Look: New Lego Set Based on the Upcoming Movie (Exclusive)|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/first-look-new-lego-set-652629|accessdate=2013-11-02|newspaper=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2013-11-01|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104073508/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/first-look-new-lego-set-652629|archivedate=2013-11-04}}</ref> 和雲鵑宮<ref name=YahooWonderKitty>{{cite news|last=Enk|first=Bryan|title=Wonder Woman Finally Gets Her Movie Close-Up ... but How Does the Lego Uni-Kitty Fit In?|url=http://movies.yahoo.com/blogs/movie-talk/superheroes-assemble-hilariously-lego-movie-trailer-214117774.html|accessdate=2013-11-02|newspaper=Yahoo! Movies|date=2013-10-31|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103051518/http://movies.yahoo.com/blogs/movie-talk/superheroes-assemble-hilariously-lego-movie-trailer-214117774.html|archivedate=2013-11-03}}</ref>，以及一套新的16個人偶<ref name=CSComicCon>{{cite news|title=Comic-Con: LEGO Announces Building Sets and Video Game for The LEGO Movie|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=106515|accessdate=2013-07-18|newspaper=ComingSoon.net|date=2013-07-16|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130731134747/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=106515|archivedate=2013-07-31}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Trumbore|first=Dave|title=New LEGO Sets Based on THE LEGO MOVIE Reveal Characters and Locations|url=http://collider.com/the-lego-movie-lego-sets-minifigures/|accessdate=2013-11-02|newspaper=Collider.com|date=2013-11-01|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103153516/http://collider.com/the-lego-movie-lego-sets-minifigures/|archivedate=2013-11-03}}</ref>。

