==市場營銷==
《樂高玩電影》收到了來自華納兄弟與樂高集團許多的營銷形式。靈感來自電影場景十七樓一套玩具的釋出，其中包括了一組珍藏人偶。開了一個網站可讓粉絲做出自己的人偶，在影片的官方預告片中。該公司已聘請全球的合作夥伴，以一個廣泛、多元的支持這部電影<ref>{{cite news|last=Strecker|first=Erin|title=Surprise! Lego group announces special sets in promotion of 'Lego Movie'|url=http://family-room.ew.com/2013/07/16/lego-special-sets-movie/|accessdate=2014-01-12|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2013-07-16|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140109193437/http://family-room.ew.com/2013/07/16/lego-special-sets-movie/|archivedate=2014-01-09}}</ref>。

官方樂高品牌專賣店也已安排，每個星期，從2014年1月，一個新的人物海報給每個購買的人<ref>{{cite news|last=|first=|title=Free exclusive 'Lego Movie' poster with any purchase!|url=http://www.freeholdracewaymall.com/Events/Details/194818?startDate=1/19/2014|accessdate=2014-01-20|publisher=Freehold Raceway Mall|date=2014-01-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201154128/http://www.freeholdracewaymall.com/Events/Details/194818?startDate=1%2F19%2F2014|archivedate=2014-02-01}}</ref>。此外[[巴諾書店|巴諾書店]]將舉辦主題活動在一月、二月和三月<ref>{{cite news|last=|first=|title=Barnes and Noble to Host In-Store Activities Campaign for 'The Lego Movie'|url=http://www.toynews-online.biz/news/read/us-barnes-noble-to-host-in-store-activities-campaign-for-the-lego-movie/041630|accessdate=2014-01-20|work=Entertainment Weekly|date=2014-01-20|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140219030334/http://www.toynews-online.biz/news/read/us-barnes-noble-to-host-in-store-activities-campaign-for-the-lego-movie/041630|archivedate=2014-02-19}}</ref>。

一款基於電影的[[電子遊戲|電子遊戲]]《[[樂高玩電影遊戲|樂高玩電影遊戲]]》，正由TT遊戲開發，平台為[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]、[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]、[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]、[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]、[[Wii_U|Wii U]]、[[Nintendo_3DS|Nintendo 3DS]]、[[PlayStation_Vita|PlayStation Vita]]和[[Windows|Windows]]，隨著電影將被釋放於2014年<ref>{{cite news|last=Purchese|first=Robert|title=TT Games doing a Lego Movie video game|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-07-16-tt-games-doing-a-lego-movie-video-game|accessdate=2014-01-12|newspaper=Eurogamer.net|date=2013-07-16|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140418043834/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-07-16-tt-games-doing-a-lego-movie-video-game|archivedate=2014-04-18}}</ref>。獨有的「狂野西部艾密特」將被釋放在Gamestop的遊戲預購<ref>{{cite web|title=LEGO Movie Videogame|url=http://www.gamestop.com/nintendo-3ds/games/lego-movie-videogame/112356|publisher=Gamestop|accessdate=2014-01-12|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140114180654/http://www.gamestop.com/nintendo-3ds/games/lego-movie-videogame/112356|archivedate=2014-01-14}}</ref>。

==發行==
《樂高玩電影》將於2014年2月6日首映在美國加州樂高樂園<ref>{{cite news|title='The Lego Movie' Event At LEGOLAND California Resort|url=http://www.thebrickfan.com/the-lego-movie-event-at-legoland-california-resort/|accessdate=2013-01-04|publisher=TheBrickFan.com|date=2014-01-03|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150330113932/http://www.thebrickfan.com/the-lego-movie-event-at-legoland-california-resort/|archivedate=2015-03-30}}</ref>，並定於在影院上映於2014年2月7日。第一部[[預告片|預告片]]發布於2013年6月18日<ref>{{cite news|title=Hot Trailer: ‘The Lego Movie’|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/06/the-lego-movie-trailer/|accessdate=2013-07-08|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2013-06-18|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130719050539/http://www.deadline.com/2013/06/the-lego-movie-trailer/|archivedate=2013-07-19}}</ref>。第二部發布於2013年10月31日，在這之前舉行了一系列特色主角的玩笑片段<ref>{{cite news|last=Nicholson|first=Max|title=The 'Lego Movie' Clip: Meet Batman|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/10/30/the-lego-movie-clip-meet-batman/|accessdate=2014-01-12|publisher=IGN|date=2013-10-30|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221223831/http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/10/30/the-lego-movie-clip-meet-batman|archivedate=2014-02-21}}</ref>。

===評價===
