2014年2月3日，加爾德·史鄧被聘為續集的撰寫<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=114356 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-02-06 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221173714/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=114356 |archivedate=2014-02-21 }}</ref>。2014年2月21日，宣布續集預計將於2018年4月發布<ref name="comingsoon1">{{cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=115163|title=The LEGO Movie Sequel is Officially Set for May 26, 2017!|publisher=ComingSoon.net|accessdate=2014-02-21|archivedate=2014-02-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140225013931/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=115163|deadurl=no}}</ref>。2014年3月12日，宣布動漫聯合導演克里斯·麥凱將和菲爾·洛德與克里斯多福·米勒一同製作續集<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/03/warner-bros-builds-lego-sequel-with-chris-mckay-directing/|title=Warner Bros Builds LEGO Sequel With Chris McKay Directing|publisher=Deadline|date=2014-03-12|accessdate=2014-03-11|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140313153825/http://www.deadline.com/2014/03/warner-bros-builds-lego-sequel-with-chris-mckay-directing/|archivedate=2014-03-13}}</ref>。華納兄弟並無邀請製片商[[威秀電影|威秀電影]]回歸參予續集<ref name=THRCutOut>{{cite web|date=2014-03-26|accessdate=2014-04-19|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/lego-movie-2-village-roadshow-691087|title='Lego Movie' Backer Village Roadshow Cut Out of Sequel (Exclusive)|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140609001113/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/lego-movie-2-village-roadshow-691087|archivedate=2014-06-09}}</ref>。後來日期改至2019年2月8日。

2017年2月，續集改由《[[魔髮精靈|魔髮精靈]]》的導演{{link-en|麥克·米契爾 (導演)|Mike Mitchell (director)|麥克·米契爾}}執導。

